  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1SA 6:1" />And the <char style="w" strong="H0727">ark</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> was in the <char style="w" strong="H7704">country</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H6430">Philistines</char> <char style="w" strong="H7651">seven</char> <char style="w" strong="H2320">months</char>. <verse eid="1SA 6:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1SA 6:2" />And the <char style="w" strong="H6430">Philistines</char> <char style="w" strong="H7121">called</char> for the <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests</char> and the <char style="w" strong="H7080">diviners</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, What shall we <char style="w" strong="H6213">do</char> to the <char style="w" strong="H0727">ark</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>? <char style="w" strong="H3045">tell</char> us wherewith we shall <char style="w" strong="H7971">send</char> it to his <char style="w" strong="H4725">place</char>. <verse eid="1SA 6:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1SA 6:3" />And they <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char>, If ye send <char style="w" strong="H7971">away</char> the <char style="w" strong="H0727">ark</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H7971">send</char> it not <char style="w" strong="H7387">empty</char>; but in any <char style="w" strong="H7725">wise</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">return</char> him a trespass <char style="w" strong="H0817">offering</char>: then ye shall be <char style="w" strong="H7495">healed</char>, and it shall be <char style="w" strong="H3045">known</char> to you why his <char style="w" strong="H3027">hand</char> is not <char style="w" strong="H5493">removed</char> from you. <verse eid="1SA 6:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1SA 6:4" />Then <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> they, What <char style