  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1SA 14:16" />And the <char style="w" strong="H6822">watchmen</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7586">Saul</char> in <char style="w" strong="H1390">Gibeah</char> of <char style="w" strong="H1144">Benjamin</char> <char style="w" strong="H7200">looked</char>; and, behold, the <char style="w" strong="H1995">multitude</char> melted <char style="w" strong="H4127">away</char>, and they <char style="w" strong="H3212">went</char> on beating <char style="w" strong="H1986">down</char> <char style="add">one another</char>. <verse eid="1SA 14:16" /><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1SA 14:17" />Then <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> <char style="w" strong="H7586">Saul</char> unto the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> that <char style="add">were</char> with him, <char style="w" strong="H6485">Number</char> now, and <char style="w" strong="H7200">see</char> who is <char style="w" strong="H1980">gone</char> from us. And when they had <char style="w" strong="H6485">numbered</char>, behold, <char style="w" strong="H3129">Jonathan</char> and his <char style="w" strong="H5375">armourbearer</char> <char style="add">were</char> not <char style="add">there</char>. <verse eid="1SA 14:17" /><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1SA 14:18" />And <char style="w" strong="H7586">Saul</char> <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H0281">Ahiah</char>, Bring <char style="w" strong="H5066">hither</char> the <char style="w" strong="H0727">ark</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char>. For the <char style="w" strong="H0727">ark</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> was at that <char style="w" strong="H3117">time</char> with the <char style="w" strong="H1121">children</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>.<verse eid="1SA 14:18" /></para>
  <para style="p">
