sid="1SA 14:32" />And the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> <char style="w" strong="H5860">flew</char> upon the <char style="w" strong="H7998">spoil</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H3947">took</char> <char style="w" strong="H6629">sheep</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1241">oxen</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1121">calves</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H7819">slew</char> <char style="add">them</char> on the <char style="w" strong="H0776">ground</char>: and the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> did <char style="w" strong="H0398">eat</char> <char style="add">them</char> with the <char style="w" strong="H1818">blood</char>.<verse eid="1SA 14:32" /></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1SA 14:33" />¶ Then they <char style="w" strong="H5046">told</char> <char style="w" strong="H7586">Saul</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, Behold, the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> <char style="w" strong="H2398">sin</char> against the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>, in that they <char style="w" strong="H0398">eat</char> with the <char style="w" strong="H1818">blood</char>. And he <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char>, Ye have <char style="w" strong="H0898">transgressed</char>: <char style="w" strong="H1556">roll</char> a <char style="w" strong="H1419">great</char> <char style="w" strong="H0068">stone</char> unto me this <char style="w" strong="H3117">day</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">14.33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">transgressed: or, dealt treacherously</char></note> <verse eid="1SA 14:33" /><verse number="34" style="v" sid="1SA 14:34" />And <char style="w" strong="H7586">Saul</char> <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6327">Disperse</char> yourselves among the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H0559">say</char> unto them, Bring me <char style="w" strong="H5066">hither</char> every <char style="w" strong="H0376">man</char> his <char style="w" strong="H7794">ox</char>, and every <char style="w" strong="H0376">man</char> his <char style="w" strong="H7716">sheep</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H7819">slay</char> <char style="add">them</char> here, and <char style="w" strong="H0398">eat</char>; and <char style="w" strong="H2398">sin</char> not against the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> in <char style="w" strong="H0398">eating</char> with the <char style="w" strong="H1818">blood</char>. And all the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> <char style="w" strong="H5066">brought</char> every <char st